Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This... isn't obligatory chocolate, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... couldn't you just make it obligatory chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean? You won't accept it if it's honmei chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher's calling for you.\NDrop by the office, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a real idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:10.17,Title,,0,0,0,,Heating up! A First Kiss in His Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Nakao-chi's information,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...Otani's stance on seeing me as a girlfriend is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean by "I don't know"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this spot right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a week, and it's still red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit me with the corner of that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was damn careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, would you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously going to go around behaving like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You might get arrested for assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. I'm the one who doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that any way to give someone honmei chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened because you said those stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "stupid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it a lot of thought before I responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just ignored me and threw the chocolate at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I opened the box, the chocolate was like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.38,Superscript,,0,0,235,,IDIOT MIDGET
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was even icing in the shape of a turd on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka switched my chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you a proper one later, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakao-chi's information #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose she was my girlfriend. Then we'd have to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's kind of comical?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something along those lines, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we see each other, it'll be in the courtroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.82,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sue you for slander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,370,298,,Defendant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Koizumi-san really get rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even rudeness has its limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that Otani-kun probably couldn't even reach Risa's lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny. It really is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that's gonna happen, anyway. We're not even dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou can't think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If confessing didn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should actively pursue him and take him by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. That might work for you, Seiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Seiko-chan, you've kissed Otani before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a nice scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I wanted to kiss him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like your love-point level is lower than an elementary student's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a kid, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never kissed anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then why do you want to be his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why," you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean isn't it so that you can walk hand in hand..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or get hot and heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as she and Otani-kun can be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yay! Umibouzu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...she'll be happy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. Everyone is so damn rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, no good. It really is comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you so damn short?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say? I'll smack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These... These...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...tickets to the Umibouzu concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for Christmas and Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,White Day would be too late, so I thought I'd give them to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I waited in line for them all morning yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What's this? Seat #3?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in the front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll even be able to distinguish Umibouzu's pores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awesome, Otani! You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, you're so manly! Otani, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he looks right at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We could shake his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll remember us from Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll even call out to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Umibouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. I humbly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when's the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I am just a kid after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since you've been on a date with just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a date or anything! There's not much romance between...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make some romance, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to let all that effort with the honmei chocolate go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal is to be a kissable girl! Chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the "chu-chu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we've been apart for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have a lot of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you were waiting to throw something at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani isn't here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard he has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I hope he's okay.\NThe concert is tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you pay him a little visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're nice to him in his weakened state, it'll leave an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weakened, weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of tomorrow's Umibouzu concert, you need to do your best now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I don't know where he lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tell you all you want to know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here ya go. A map to his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I get it. I'm gonna go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even do things that might result in you catching his cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here are the report cards for you second-year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.68,Default,,30,0,310,,Otani
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm Otani-kun's classmate, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't at school today, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...I came to visit him and brought his report card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you A-chan's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A-chan's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a beauty too, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy's been practically dead since this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he's a bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan! A-chan, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea. It'll just be a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are you feeling... A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan, what good timing.\NLet's have some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just picked it up. It's round.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute while I cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't feed a sick person cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? That's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are tall, aren't you.\NHow tall are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... 172 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,172?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shorter than her, A-chan. How uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's not scared by your shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't even tall enough to kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your girlfriend, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday today, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You should at least know the birthday of the guy you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Your report card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. It's about as bad as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And, here. Some oranges to help you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'll be okay tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For Umibouzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't go, then just go by yourself. Enjoy it for me, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going, then I won't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point if I don't get to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? I went to a lot of effort to get those tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to come, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you start liking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can you ask something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me to say whatever is on my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I expect this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you always talking about how short I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want a boyfriend this short?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously going to hit you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts... What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you want a tall girl like me for a girlfriend either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, height has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it does... I guess it does a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me not to think about height, and just go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it last summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own charm, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be indecisive. Just go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not mind? Of course I mind, being the only one who doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when you didn't know it was you, and you were going around asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who does Koizumi like?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that supposed to me be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My face doesn't look like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you treat the guy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't taunt a sick person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really as concerned with height as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's because of my twisted personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that, then you should do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd be weird if you changed all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the problem lies with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the two of us are alone in this room right now, I don't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really that unattractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko-Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I forgot to give you sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um, I'll be leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan? What happened, A-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I'm completely cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. My fever came back again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the last thing I remember was eating oranges. It's all a blank after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Koizumi, did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Koizumi, did you catch a cold?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's all a blank after that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the weather sure is nice today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect for an Umibouzu concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,L-O-V-E Maity!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Koizumi is acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away. All I can see right now is that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: A Killer Crush on Maity!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
